@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
actor "Khách hàng" as User
participant "profile.html + ProfileService (JS)" as Frontend
participant "UserController" as Controller
participant "UserServiceImpl" as Service
participant "ICustomerRepository" as CustomerRepo
participant "IMembershipTierRepository" as TierRepo
participant "IAvatarService" as AvatarService

User -> Frontend: 1. Click "Tài khoản" trên header
Frontend -> Controller: 2. GET /api/users/me
Controller -> Service: 3. getMyProfile(username)
Service -> CustomerRepo: 4. findByUsername(username)
Service -> TierRepo: 5. findTopByMinPointLessThanEqualOrderByMinPointDesc(point)
Service -> Service: 6. refreshTier() + setMembershipTier
Service --> Controller: 7. UserProfileResponse
Controller --> Frontend: 8. 200 OK + JSON
Frontend -> Frontend: 9. renderProfile() (sidebar, form, membership grid)

== Upload Avatar ==
User -> Frontend: 10. Chọn file avatar + nhấn "Tải ảnh lên"
Frontend -> AvatarService: 11. handleUploadAvatar()
AvatarService -> Controller: 12. POST /api/users/me/avatar (MultipartFile)
Controller -> AvatarServiceImpl: 13. uploadAvatar(file, username)
AvatarServiceImpl -> CustomerRepo: 14. findByUsername()
AvatarServiceImpl -> Cloudinary: 15. uploader().upload()
AvatarServiceImpl -> CustomerRepo: 16. save(customer) với avatarUrl mới
AvatarServiceImpl --> Controller: 17. AvatarUploadResponse
Controller --> Frontend: 18. 200 OK
Frontend -> Frontend: 19. Cập nhật preview + localStorage + dispatch "profile-updated"

== Cập nhật Thông tin ==
User -> Frontend: 20. Chỉnh sửa thông tin + nhấn "Lưu thay đổi"
Frontend -> Controller: 21. PUT /api/users/me (UpdateProfileRequest)
Controller -> Service: 22. updateMyProfile(username, request)
Service -> CustomerRepo: 23. findByUsername() + save()
Service --> Controller: 24. UserProfileResponse mới
Controller --> Frontend: 25. 200 OK
Frontend -> Frontend: 26. renderProfile() + updateHeaderUI()

User <-- Frontend: 27. Hoàn tất quản lý tài khoản cá nhân
@enduml